 The candidate of the Peoples Democratic Party, PDP, in the February 23, 2019, presidential election, Alhaji Atiku Abubakar, has finally spoken to Nigerians weeks after the Presidential election Tribunal quashed his claims and evidences against President Muhammadu Buhari of the All Progressives Congress, APC. Continue reading Breaking: Finally, Atiku speaks after tribunal judgment, says nothing good comes easy at Vanguard News. Source: Vanguard